Products Co-Chairman Bettiann Gardner of Chicago; and Beulah Mae
Donald of Mobile, Ala., winner of a $7 million lawsuit against white
supremacists.
   Ms. Donald died in September.
   The awards were announced at a ceremony Tuesday at the Chicago
Theatre.
