<HEAD>Drug Suspected In More Than 20 Deaths</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PITTSBURGH (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Federal and state authorities are investigating
more than 20 deaths linked to the illegal use of the heroin
substitute China White in the Pittsburgh area.
   U.S. Attorney J. Alan Johnson said Tuesday the death toll
