<HEAD>USDA Says New Grain Deal With Soviets Near</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A long-awaited new grain deal with the Soviet
Union may be near, Agriculture Department spokesmen said late
Wednesday.
