<HEAD>Auto Production Down This Week</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DETROIT (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Domestic automakers were scheduled to produce
138,669 cars and light trucks this week, down from last week's
254,869, Ward's Automotive Reports said Wednesday.
   This week's production is lower than the same week a year ago, in
which 140,776 cars and light trucks were produced, the trade journal
said.
